und to reach the round of 16.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her nerve\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the win-clinching point\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Catantan said she endured mobility problems after hurting her left knee in theround of 64,where she clinched a come-from-behind 15-13 win over Brazil's Mariana Pistoia.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7427653170795895, \"rank\": 0.34394543403379035, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"score\": 0.9997201117141754, \"rank\": 0.0002799558134957893, \"text\": \"Pistoia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Catantan\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"mobility problems\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"her left knee\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"theround\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"a come-from-behind 15-13 win\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Penn State standoutinjuredthe same knee in the Southeast Asian Games in Phnom Penh, Cambodia, last year and got sidelined for nearly 10 months.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2036, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"